den Tätigkeiten ausleuchtet.  aWhat do people do when they work in projects? This book shows that projects stand for independent and creative yet also for strictly controlled work. That contradiction is resolved in work that organizes.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aArbeit. 4aArbeits- und Industriesoziologie. 4aOrganisationssoziologie. 4aPlanung. 4aProjektarbeit. 4aProjekte. 4aProjektmanagement. 4aProjektorganisation. 4aSelbstorganisation. 4aSoziologie. 4aSoziologische Theorie. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh  aPlanning.  aProject Work.  aProjects.  aSelf-organization.  aSociological Theory.  aSociology of Organizations.  aSociology of Work and Industry.  aSociology.  aWork.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2018z978311071955008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2018z9783110603231oZDB-23-DSW40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839441565zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839441565423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839441565/original  a978-3-11-071955-0  DG Plus eBook-Package 2018b2018  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-DSWb2018